00:33:25,454 --> 00:33:30,473
Speaker 0: If they don't match either you were wrong in the output tape, you wrote by hand or the program is wrong.

564
00:33:31,035 --> 00:33:36,677
Speaker 0: And you just keep running through different input tapes and match them up to the appropriate output tapes.

